    public abstract class AbstractStepPresenter
extends java.lang.Object
implements MenuListener, VaadinViewPresenter
    Project: Masterthesis of Sascha Feldmann Creation date: 23.05.2016 Author: Sascha Feldmann (sascha.feldmann@gmx.de)

    University: Hochschule f√ºr Technik und Wirtschaft, Berlin Fachbereich 4 Studiengang Internationale Medieninformatik (Master)

    Company: adesso AG

    This abstract presenter defines the basic components that each view in the application has, e.g. the current step indicator etc. It is a MenuListener and therefore manages menu clicks.
